[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0993","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0667","title":"ARP 协议 ARP 缓存投毒 拒绝服务欺骗漏洞","description":"ARP 协议缺乏身份验证机制，允许局域网内任意主机伪造 ARP 回复包投毒 ARP 缓存，导致 IP 地址欺骗或拒绝服务攻击。攻击者只需接入同一广播域，发送伪造的 ARP 应答将目标 IP 映射到攻击者 MAC 地址，即可劫持流量、窃取数据或中断通信。该漏洞影响所有使用标准 ARP 协议的 IPv4 网络设备，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0667"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.363","remediation":"在交换机上启用动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 和 DHCP Snooping 功能，对关键服务器配置静态 ARP 条目，部署 ARP 欺骗检测工具（如 arpwatch），并在主机侧启用数据包签名或使用 IPSec 加密通信以缓解 ARP 缓存投毒攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602880019797&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d0ba8eaeba3ff3558e6044a19d5b454dcc12f33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0667.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0667","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/e308a62e3fd448dc7e655afff41cb1de4b41d101/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0667.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e54d5f68d5b83411d51ab3df8f5c1b120360f139/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0667.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/a882eda2674c920d46c962c584db177720af345c/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/based2/KB/blob/c9cae949a7a9adb4f8bf8a6864a48f7defc467d7/security/vulnerabities.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0667.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88350/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1343","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1343.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1125","title":"Oracle Webserver 2.1 及更早版本 setuid root 配置权限提升漏洞","description":"Oracle Webserver 2.1 及更早版本以 setuid root 权限运行，但配置文件归 oracle 账户所有。任何获得 oracle 账户访问权限的本地或远程攻击者均可通过修改配置文件，利用 setuid root 权限提升至 root 权限，或修改任意文件，造成系统完全失陷。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1125"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1997-09-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Oracle Webserver 2.1 以上版本，或将配置文件所有权改为 root 用户并移除 oracle 账户的写权限，避免配置被低权限用户篡改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T02:09:59.999800886+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602880019796&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1343.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1239","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0956","title":"NeXT NetInfo _writers 属性本地权限提升与拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NeXT NetInfo 的 _writers 属性存在本地权限提升与拒绝服务漏洞。拥有本地普通用户权限的攻击者可通过滥用 _writers 属性以 root 身份执行任意操作，或触发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 NeXTSTEP 和 OPENSTEP 操作系统，攻击条件简单，仅需具备本地用户账户即可完成利用，CVSS v2 评分为 7.2，对系统的机密性、完整性和可用性均造成完全损害。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0956"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-19","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 NeXTSTEP/OPENSTEP 操作系统，无官方补丁。应将系统迁移至受支持的现代操作系统（如 macOS、Linux）；短期内应禁用不必要的本地用户账户、限制物理接触、通过防火墙禁止远程登录以降低本地利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0956","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0956.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0956.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0956.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1403","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1403.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1214","title":"FreeBSD 内核异步 I/O 凭证校验缺失导致本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"4.4 BSD 内核中的异步 I/O 机制存在权限校验缺失漏洞。在设置 I/O 通知信号的接收进程时，内核未对用户凭证进行检查，导致本地攻击者可通过特定的 ioctl 和 fcntl 系统调用，将信号发送到任意进程 ID。本地低权限用户无需特殊授权即可利用此漏洞，向任意进程（包括高权限系统进程）发送信号，从而干扰或终止其正常运行，最终引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响基于 4.4 BSD 内核的 FreeBSD 等操作系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级较低，利用需具备本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1214"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.743","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至 4.4-RELEASE 或更高版本（已修补该内核异步 I/O 权限校验缺陷）。若暂无法升级，可通过内核参数限制普通用户对 ioctl/fcntl 的调用权限，或在防火墙层面限制本地特权用户滥用信号发送接口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.com/advisories/signals.txt","http://www.osvdb.org/11062","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/556","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c7dbcfe83bb4dc502ef05181d3fc65159afa615a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1214.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1214","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1214.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/fb79aaf8eeeb3ec551114292cd7a8693e166aee6/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1214.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2wrh-h883-mcp8/GHSA-2wrh-h883-mcp8.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88608/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1214.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--142fad7b-6c79-49ea-b725-b5b8c343ccc0.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1403.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0192","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0079","title":"Sun Solaris 7/8 FTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7 和 Solaris 8 系统的 FTP 服务器存在资源耗尽漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送大量 PASV 命令，导致服务器可用端口被迅速耗尽，从而使合法用户无法建立新的数据连接，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用门槛低，仅需网络可达即可触发，影响运行上述 Solaris 版本的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0079"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.890","remediation":"建议安装 Sun 官方补丁 ID 106222-02 (Solaris 7) 或 106223-02 (Solaris 8)，限制单连接内 PASV 命令的并发端口数。也可在 in.ftpd 配置中降低 PASV 最小端口范围或缩短空闲端口超时。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 控制连接速率作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0079"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1444","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1444.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1275","title":"Lotus cc:Mail 明文密码存储权限提升漏洞","description":"Lotus cc:Mail 8 版本存在密码明文存储漏洞，系统将邮箱服务器密码以明文形式存储于隐藏文件中，且该文件权限配置不当，本地普通用户可读取该文件获取管理员密码，进而实现权限提升。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限即可利用该漏洞，影响范围限于 Lotus cc:Mail 8 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，属于中危漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1275"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.443","remediation":"Lotus cc:Mail 8 已停止维护，无官方补丁，建议迁移至 IBM Domino 或受支持的邮件系统；暂无法迁移时，收紧 cc:Mail 隐藏口令文件（如 .cclm）权限为 600（仅属主读写），并通过系统 ACL 禁止非管理员用户读取该文件，同时使用主机防火墙限制本地非授权进程的网络访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9478","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1619","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1275.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1275","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1275.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1275.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7mxx-wrm5-32f9/GHSA-7mxx-wrm5-32f9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87812/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1275.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/839e2559933f5ff6cd50b4768fd382827d790668/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1444.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0374","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0191","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 newdsn.exe 文件创建漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 的 newdsn.exe CGI 脚本存在文件创建/覆盖漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求利用此脚本，在服务器上任意创建或覆盖文件，可能导致系统配置被篡改或敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击复杂度较低，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0191"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.367","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 3.0 服务器上的 newdsn.exe 文件或将其所在 cgi-bin 目录权限设置为禁止匿名访问；同时升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本以彻底消除该 CGI 脚本，或迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并启用最新安全配置。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 过滤规则拦截对 newdsn.exe 的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/275","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20309","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0191","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0191.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p6cp-hx87-7342/GHSA-p6cp-hx87-7342.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0191.yaml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/newdsn.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0374.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0374.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0353","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0177","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 服务器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WebSite Web 服务器中的 uploader 程序存在任意文件上传漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的上传请求，将恶意可执行文件上传至服务器任意目录并远程执行，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响早期版本的 WebSite 服务器软件，攻击者只需能够网络访问目标服务器即可发起攻击，利用方式简单、危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0177"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.913","remediation":"建议立即升级至 O'Reilly WebSite Professional 2.x（该版本已修复 uploader 漏洞）；如无法升级，可直接删除或禁用 webroot 下的 uploader.exe/cgi 程序，并在 Web 服务器或防火墙层面限制对 uploader 相关路径的访问。由于该产品已终止技术支持（EOL），长期解决方案是迁移至仍在安全维护期的 Web 服务器（如 Apache、Nginx 或 IIS）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0177"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0258","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0115","title":"IBM AIX bugfiler 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x 操作系统中的 bugfiler 程序存在任意文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可创建或覆盖系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 3.x 版本，攻击者仅需本地账户即可利用，无需用户交互，危害较高，CVSS 评分 7.2。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0115"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.230","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.1.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续发行版中修复。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/bugfiler` 移除 setuid 特权位，防止本地用户通过 bugfiler 获取 root Shell；若无需使用 bugfiler 工具，可直接 `chmod 700 /usr/bin/bugfiler` 限制仅 root 可执行。请评估是否需同时更新 `bos.rte.security` 文件集的相关安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1800","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0115","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0115.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0422","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0422.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0237","title":"Guestbook CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Guestbook CGI 程序（Matt Wright 编写的 Perl 脚本）未对用户输入进行充分过滤和转义，远程攻击者可通过向表单字段提交特制的 shell 元字符实现命令注入，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务进程权限执行任意命令。此漏洞无需身份认证，利用门槛低，攻击者仅需构造恶意 HTTP 请求即可入侵服务器。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响大量使用该 CGI 程序的老旧 Web 服务器。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0237"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即删除或更换服务器上的 guestbook.cgi 脚本，该 CGI 程序已停止维护且无官方补丁。对用户输入进行严格过滤，移除 shell 元字符（|;`$等）。建议使用现代留言板系统替代，或通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 ScriptAlias 或 Nginx 禁止 CGI 执行）彻底禁用此脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0237","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0237","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0237.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p9x6-hv6c-rpfx/GHSA-p9x6-hv6c-rpfx.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/guestbook.nasl","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0237.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80893/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0422.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0366","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0366.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0183","title":"Linux TFTP 实现目录遍历漏洞","description":"Linux系统的TFTP（Trivial File Transfer Protocol）实现中存在目录遍历漏洞，未限制文件访问路径。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过路径穿越技术访问TFTP根目录之外的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露，如密码文件等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0183"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复此漏洞的TFTP服务器版本（如tftp-hpa），或配置chroot环境将TFTP服务限制在指定目录内，并禁用符号链接跟随以防止目录遍历攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T21:58:50.651362824+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0366.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0302","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0302.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0148","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 CGI 处理程序远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统自带的 cgi-bin 处理器程序 handler 存在命令注入漏洞。该 CGI 程序未能正确过滤用户提供的 URL 参数，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，在受影响服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意系统命令。攻击复杂度低且无需身份验证，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0148"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5 或更高版本以修复 cgi-bin handler 的命令注入漏洞。如无法升级，在 /etc/cgi-bin/handler 配置中移除不必要的 CGI 映射，并在网络层面限制对 CGI 端口的访问。若环境允许，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/380","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19303"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19303"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0302.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0302.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0179","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0179.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0071","title":"Apache HTTP Server Cookie 处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.1.1 及更早版本的 cookie 处理函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未对输入长度进行充分校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 Cookie 数据触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致 httpd 进程崩溃或潜在远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有运行受影响 Apache httpd 版本的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0071"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 cookie 处理函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。由于 1.2.0 版本也已停止维护，建议迁移至当前受支持的 Apache HTTP Server 版本（如 2.4.x），以确保获得持续的安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0071","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0179.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1411","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1411.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1220","title":"Majordomo 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Majordomo 1.94.3 及更早版本存在远程命令执行漏洞。当邮件列表配置文件中使用了 advertise 或 noadvertise 指令时，未经过身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在邮件的 Reply-To（回复地址）头部中嵌入 Shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）突破程序的安全过滤。目标系统将 Reply-To 头部内容传递给底层 Shell 处理时会执行攻击者注入的任意命令，从而实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有使用存在缺陷版本 Majordomo 且配置了 advertise/noadvertise 指令的邮件列表服务器，攻击条件仅需向列表发送一封构造了恶意 Reply-To 头部的邮件，利用门槛较低，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1220"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-08-24T04:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.500Z","remediation":"升级 Majordomo 到 1.94.4 或更高版本，新版本对 Reply-To 头部中的 Shell 元字符进行了过滤处理，可消除此漏洞。如暂时无法升级，应在配置文件中移除或注释掉 advertise 和 noadvertise 指令，避免漏洞被触发。同时建议审查现有邮件列表配置，确认没有暴露于恶意构造的 Reply-To 头部攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/7527","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/502","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1220.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1220","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1220.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/666a3c9c944f5ed9f7d7ff0aa29b047387ce02f3/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1220.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-95g2-fv7p-pc5j/GHSA-95g2-fv7p-pc5j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88588/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1220.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000203.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1411.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1414","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1414.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1225","title":"Linux/Ultrix NFS rpc.mountd 文件存在性信息泄露漏洞","description":"rpc.mountd（NFS 挂载守护进程）在处理挂载请求时，会根据被请求导出目录下的文件或目录是否存在而返回不同的错误信息。攻击者可通过向 rpc.mountd 发送针对特定文件或目录的挂载请求，依据返回差异判断目标系统上文件或目录是否存在，从而实现对服务器文件系统的信息探测。该漏洞本身不导致任意文件读取或代码执行，但可被用于辅助后续攻击、枚举敏感文件路径。攻击条件为攻击者需能与目标主机的 RPC 端口（通常为 111 及 NFS 相关端口）进行网络连通。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1225"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-24","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"对于运行受影响版本 NFS 工具包的 Linux 系统，建议将 nfs-utils 升级至厂商已修复该漏洞的最新版本，较新的发行版中 rpc.mountd 已统一文件不存在的错误返回信息，不再泄露文件是否存在。如当前系统无需提供 NFS 导出服务，可直接禁用 rpc.mountd 守护进程并在防火墙中封锁 TCP 和 UDP 2049 端口及 RPC 端口映射器（端口 111），以彻底消除攻击面。对于 Ultrix 等旧版系统，建议联系厂商获取补丁或迁移至受支持的现代操作系统版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/7526","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/347","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/431324351d69005e5e9ea9d116dc965ce92ed482/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1225.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1414.toml"}]